input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT s.NCESSchool, s.School, f.\"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\" FROM frpm f JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode WHERE f.\"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY f.\"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\" DESC LIMIT 10;"
